      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite achieving gradation 4 SQA compliance under FDA software guidance.",
      "rationale": "OpenFOAM v8 with hemolysis UDF is tracked in a git repository with CI regression tests covering 95% of solver paths. SQA documentation satisfies gradation 4 requirements for MRL 5."
    },
    {
