      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid viscosity) documented and matched to simulation inputs within stated uncertainty bands.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump bench tests conducted at 4 L/min ± 0.05 L/min and 2500 RPM ± 10 RPM with bovine blood viscosity characterised. Simulation boundary conditions set to match within these bands. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
