      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g. NRMSE or E_rel) below 15% for hemolysis index and velocity magnitude across all validation cases.",
      "rationale": "Normalised RMS error on hemolysis index is 9.2% across five operating points; velocity magnitude NRMSE is 7.6% against PIV data. Gradation 4 output comparison criterion satisfied."
