      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model selection justified by literature evidence and sensitivity analysis demonstrating robustness.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark comparisons for rotating machinery; Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law calibrated against independent dataset. Sensitivity analysis shows NIH varies by less than 12% across three candidate model forms. Gradation 4 achieved."
