      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material and geometric input parameters characterised with quantified uncertainty; Monte Carlo propagation performed.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis model exponents characterised with distributions from literature meta-analysis. 1000-sample Monte Carlo propagation yields 95th-percentile NIH uncertainty band of ±18%. Gradation 4 model-inputs criterion satisfied."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
